{"type":null,"faqId":33945,"title":"为什么手机能唤醒，但语音识别（如打电话指令）却总是提示不成功？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">唤醒是由于唤醒词经过了您的特别训练,所以能够有更好的识别率。而唤醒之后的指令种类较多，同一个命令也可以有多重表达方式（如打电话给小华，给小华打电话等），所以无法一一进行强化训练。另外，受限于您所在的环境嘈杂程度以及说话的语速、口音等，所以效果上无法确保跟唤醒一样的识别成功率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为了获得较好的识别成功率，建议尝试：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1）请尽量使用标准普通话说出语音指令</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2）在您说完唤醒词后，稍作停顿再说指令时可获得更好的识别成功率</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3）如果首次没有能够识别，等待提示结束后你可再次输入指令</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8647","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748769000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":33,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,语音识别","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}